import React from "react";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

import { Button, TextField, Grid } from "@material-ui/core";

import useStyles from "../utils/stylesRegister";

export default function BookEdit({ book }) {
  console.log(book);
  const classes = useStyles();
  return (
    <form className={classes.form} /*onSumbit={onSubmit}*/>
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
          <TextField
            /*   onChange={handleChange} */
            autoComplete="fname"
            name="nombre"
            variant="outlined"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="firstName"
            label="Titulo"
            autoFocus
            defaultValue={book.titulo}
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
          <TextField
            /*     onChange={handleChange} */
            variant="outlined"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="lastName"
            label="Autor"
            name="apellido"
            autoComplete=""
            defaultValue={book.autor}
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <TextField
            A
            variant="outlined"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="email"
            label="Categoria"
            name="email"
            autoComplete="email"
            defaultValue={book.editorial}
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <TextField
            /*   onChange={handleChange} */
            variant="outlined"
            required
            fullWidth
            name="password"
            label="Precio"
            id="password"
            autoComplete="current-password"
            defaultValue={book.precio}
          />
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
      <Button
        type="submit"
        fullWidth
        variant="contained"
        color="primary"
        className={classes.submit}
      >
        Enviar Info
      </Button>
    </form>
  );
}
